                    <img src="https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=User&background=random" alt="User Avatar">
                </span>
                <span class="user-message">Imaginary Hub AI, make a content calendar for my marketing campaign.</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="assistant-message">
                <div>Of course. Here's the calendar!</div>
                
